{"tid":2094051,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【貼地城嫂】方媛淡妝迫地鐵：我是上班族啊！","createTime":"2020-07-04T09:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T14:50:04.000Z","uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac8b64eab44e550c89d690bcd87c299ab78c9ff","tid":2094051,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200704/356082585862017025.jpeg/KniBTQGbhFsGUvKuuStRTmKe9ru90BkaWffkq1n35Ks?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200704%2F356082585862017025.jpeg%2FKniBTQGbhFsGUvKuuStRTmKe9ru90BkaWffkq1n35Ks%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7a182c6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1165e7e7bcff974ed38c4f6f0f3fc57729a7df3","tid":2094051,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"32歲方媛（Moka）自2017年成為郭富城太太後，三年抱兩誕下兩名女兒，婚後相夫教女，同時積極融入香港生活。今日城嫂方媛在社交網貼了一張自拍照，相中的她戴住口罩，長髮披肩，穿搭簡約，只畫了眉毛，妝容極淡，身處人來人往的地鐵站，留言︰「下班高峰，haha我像不像上班族。」<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，城城擁有多部名車，更曾被拍到揸林寶堅尼落銅鑼灣買尿片給囡囡。估唔到雖然老公的名車多到數唔到，但城嫂竟然願意迫地鐵出入，獲網民大讚夠貼地，有網民留言︰「做全職太太多無聊啊，自己還是需要有自己的事情做。」方媛亦有留言回應對方：「我是上班族啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」"},{"pid":"f879dcd34e98282d3734adf0f0c60c113e10fad2","tid":2094051,"uid":209657,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200704/356127927995338752.jpeg/TMY5VYtUaDaC9q9q3fV1TFngQNB0eEOGD6NcdQ-jXHU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200704%2F356127927995338752.jpeg%2FTMY5VYtUaDaC9q9q3fV1TFngQNB0eEOGD6NcdQ-jXHU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=feadb9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200521/340238688111955968.jpeg/mem-kA0Yt_TJnyqfbeX5TqXmATbG6xZLEe6NEBHujRA?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.co